Terry Brooks does some great books if you haven't read them. The Shannara series is excellent but there are certain books that stand out. His Running with the Demon series is very cool as well. I'm eagerly looking forward to his new book coming out this fall, in the meantime I'm reading Dennis L. Mc Kiernan's Iron Tower series (one volume now). Decent book so far. <p>Cerranshaun Lightbringer<br>
